-   `c(1, 1L, "C")`


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
c(1, 1L, "C")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "1" "1" "C"
```
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
1
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 1
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
1L
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 1
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
"C"
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "C"
```
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
#typeof(c(1, 1L, "C"))
```
:::


-   `c(1L / 0, "A")`


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
c(1L / 0, "A")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "Inf" "A"  
```
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(1L)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "integer"
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(0)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "double"
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(1L/0)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "double"
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof("A")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "character"
```
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
#typeof(c(1L / 0, "A"))
```
:::
